{"text": "The development that the Hitman games have been going through is amazing.  With this game you don't only get some very nice graphics but also a great game experience.  You have a lot of freedom in which ways you wish to complete the missions the game offers you. Whether you wish to go full stealth mode or 'breach and clear' is up to you, though if you want a high score you should stick to the stealthy and creative ways. Furthermore there's a lot of challenges in each mission you can go for to challenge yourself even more (and get a better score, if you want to top your friends scores).  The amount of missions aren't big.  However, due to so many possibilities you have in each of the missions it actually makes up for the little amount of different missions the standard game offers.  If you like games where stealth and creativity are on the list then this game is definitely worth for you to consider, especially now when the Steam Summer Sale is ongoing.", "appid": "236870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198024990117", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0}
