{"text": "This game is a masterpiece. There are tons of weapons with different strengths and weaknesses and different move sets to choose from and each one of them is actually useful. The game does not force feed the story to the player, he actually has to travel through the world to understand the story behind each character in the game and it is just amazing what you can discover. Everything in this game, from the location of a certain item to the position of a certain enemy, has its own little story. A lot of the content is optional so this game is just great for every adventurer. I have played this game with multiple characters over a few months but I still discover a few secrets that I missed the other times. This game is quite difficult but it is fair. Even common enemies can wipe the floor with you if you havenÂ´t figured out how to fight them but it is relatively easy once you have figured it out and the satisfaction of beating a boss for the first time after dozens of deaths cannot be described.", "appid": "211420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198015133785", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1390996800.0}
