{"text": "I think this game is underrated.  It is a beautiful cyberpunk game that has a little bit of everything - good story, strong female lead, interesting characters, detailed environment, puzzles, platforming, combat system with customization, and creative elements.   I can understand some of the complaints about repetitiveness of combat and linear levels, but other good story-driven games are like that too.   I guess it is a matter of perspective.   If you are like me and don't finish games in one sit-down, those complaints probably won't matter much.  I actually couldn't wait for my next break so I could continue the story.  On sale, this game is a steal imho.", "appid": "228300", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970495096", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "69", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1425816000.0}
