{"text": "READ THIS BEFORE PURCHASING !!! I'm a big fan of Shadow of Mordor and i've waited for Shadow of War to be accesible (price) for me. Here are my pros and cons : ***Pros :  -Bigger map -Better skill tree -The orcs are not so dumb anymore and they are actually pretty decent damage delears, except when they fight for you in an arena, there they are dumb as a rock and miss almost all the attack, a normal orc managed to kill a legendary one who was 5 levels higher. -It's pretty hard to master but after you get the hang of it you will be hardER to kill, don't think you won't die :)) especially if you play on Nemesis difficulty. -They did improve some features and others stuff + you get to do a lot more missions with orcs or with Talion. ***Cons: -The orcs are f*cking writes now... when they see you they start writing love stories that keep the cut scene for 10-50 seconds in which they describe the love for your or other intetions.And there are a lot of messages that they carry, A LOT. You'll get bored of them and you'll try to end them before they enter cut-scene. -After you capture a captain they'll say very few things AND i mean like 4-5 words , 4-5 sentences. Comparing to when they see you, this is crap... i mean they can say : \"I'll watch you hang from your bowels while drinking grog\" but they can't say anything else except \"I'm yours Bright Lord\" and \"I am your chosen\". In 34 hours i've met only one captain that said \"My life is yours\" while the others captains said the first 2 sentences i've said above or another 2 that i can't remember now. -It became like Assasin's Creed.... very repetitive... you can't invade a region with the army from another region so you'll have to go captain shopping again on every region until you got yourself an army. -No improvements on graphics -In pit fights the orc you own is dumbed down hard, it takes 2 roll overs, 3 taunts, 4 yelling and 5 turn arounds to hit once while the other orc is going berserk on your orc. -When you capture a warchief he doesn't stay a warchief, so he'll have to fight again to become one. This is dumb, even retarded. When you capture a captain he doesn't go back to being a grunt, he stays as a captain. What happend to : \" ME.KILL.YOU\" or \"YOU DIE\" ???? <<< This was a lot better because the cut scene would be 2-3 seconds, not a full minute of love making stories. My opinion : Buy it for lower than 13 euros , the gold edition and only if you're a fan. If you want to buy this without playing Shadow of Mordor then don't . Don't buy it because you'll get bored of it.", "appid": "356190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198022082358", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1532865600.0}
