{"text": "It's been one of the best games that I have played so far in 2018, despite being a low budget title and is coming from a quite well-known publisher which is known for being obviously less-than-stellar, especially in how they began, yet given the universal acclaim that it's been getting and the fact that it's selling like hot cakes, this may be not only their break-trough title, but also their absolute BEST release so far. I also sincerely fell in love with the miko named Yoko (As she is also visible on the game's thumbnail) because of her amazing apperance, given the game's fabulous 2D graphical presentation, which is very impressive for a game that has fairly low production values, yet still manages to be great even if the production values, given its a budget title, are low; not to mention, her very well-fitting, Senran Kagura-like BGM, given the fact that the music in the game is also great to listen to. Since the game is being universally acclaimed, given that I am also acclaiming it for all the top qualities it has despite being fairly low budget, and that I've been in love with Yoko since I first played it after I bought it, especially since I also had some good fun messing around with her after fighting her three times or even the fourth to have a very long good time with her ( Í¡Â° ÍœÊ– Í¡Â°) , except that there's no way to kiss her, unlike in Senran Kagura :( , I am definetely looking forward to not only a sequel to this game with further additions or refinements, or even a spin-off to this game focusing on the one miko herself alone, but also to many other eroge titles, especially those on Steam, in the years to come, which would have hybrid animation like this game already has, the ability to mess around with the girls while also kissing them (Which this game should have had, but perhaps save for sequels if possible), and also very beautifully-looking girls like Yoko, but even more beautiful and gorgeous. HuniePop, you have a new competitor....... Valkyrie Drive: Bhikkhuni............you were very disappointing, and you Rinka, Ranka and Mana, also a miko, just as much so. But this game, and also Yoko herself, totally redeem me at a high level.", "appid": "644560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011120041", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530878400.0}
