{"text": "It is a scrolling game, where you need to beat your quad/endure bike enemies with your speed or with the brute force before the time finishes or the finish lap. We have two modalities:   and  .  In quick mode, you can choose the type of race you will do, while the divided into seasons (5 in total) while the career doesnâ€™t need an explanation. In the career mode, in hard mode, without any sort of booster, the challenge is very high: In some levels, if you make a little mistake, you need to restart it because you will not able to win it.  For this reason, I loved this game a lot: Who want a very hard challenge could play it all in hard while who are searching a casual game, normal is not that hard and donâ€™t lead the player to rage quit and uninstall the game. As I said, the game is very optimized also about the compatibility of controller: without lag and all the keys work perfectly. In fact, in this game the precision and change of the direction is fundamental to win over the enemies. The game has a cartoon ambience but very detailed. In every season, there are some new things that donâ€™t annoy you to be like and always in the same environment (such as pizza boys, more powerful police, endure bikes ect..) -The devs are open to improve their game with ideas and fixing some eventual bug.  -They always answer you for any problem in the steam hub. -I also helped to improve some levels in game and some little bugs and I did it because I saw    a lot of potential in this game. That time i did a good choice ;D Every week there is, in the LiveWire mode, the possibility to win steam gift cards if you do the best time in the leaderboard against the other players.   Proof of the wallet received:", "appid": "1099440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198153982287", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "33", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1572609600.0}
