{"text": "I was really hyped for this game and got dissapointed. Since the first announcement I was waiting for this game and at first I really tried to love it, but the more I played I realized that there are too many issues I can't ignore and ruin the fun I normally have in fighting games. You can tell that they kind of rushed this game and that it's not complete. Let me give you a list of issues I have with this game. -Ranked system is more like a grinding system where you grind points. You get a lot of points and lose like nothing. - Matchmaking is bad aswell you fight even as high rank totally low rank players but maybe I can understand that because the ranking system is not about who is good player more like who plays the most. -People can actually cheat like crazy if they want (not going to say more about this here) -Every second match is lagging like crazy and there are a lot of network issues. No settings are going to help you sadly. I feel like the function to set +4 bars is not even working because it literally changed nothing. -Most people think that the graphics are beautiful. I disagree if you look at the textures in detail. They didn't even animated the eye on Nightmares sword. -Story Mode got like 2 real cutsences the rest are just Pictures with text. Feels like a low budget Visual Novel. -Reversal Edge is a rock paper scissors mechanic that no one needs and you have to watch a cutscene every single time. -Critical Edge Long cutscenes and it's stronger then in tekken 7 and you can use it not only near death. That means you see it a lot. -Too many cutscenes per fight sometimes I feel like I watch a movie rather then playing a fighting game thanks to soulcharge,gi, critical edge, reversal edge and in other things slow motions during the fight. -Bugs that can make a character broken -Small character roster -CaS where you can change hitboxes and things like dmg for range and can use it in ranked or just use big props that you can't see the characters moves anymore. -If you're unlucky you're rank get's randomly resetted -There are only 2 Online modes Ranked/Rooms -Not enough offline content -No music that is memorable -No memorable stages -No detailed profile stats  -DLC day1. -With some characters I can just go ranked mash buttons without knowing anything and go on 10 winstreak. I think on some characters the moves they have are just too much. So many safe moves low risk high reward. Characters with long range mixups with high dmg, a one hit move to instantly ringout someone from everywhere and much more. Many times it doesn't feel like I played well to win a match or my opponent played well. Maybe this game is really good at high lvl (tournaments no delay) but not as a average player ONLINE. In my opinion it's not worth to get this game for the full price of 60$ Maybe wait for 50% Sale in the meanwhile they are going to fix some of the issues hopefully.", "appid": "544750", "steamid": "profiles/76561197988945061", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "47", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1541678400.0}
