{"text": "Before anything I need to say that I've played X-COM UFO Defense extensively back then, the new one and it's sequel. I enjoy FF Tactics very much and even Rebelstar: Tactical Command. I really wanted to dig this one from what I had seen before the release :(. It would have been awesome this art style with some better tactical mechanics... It's more like basic puzzles than tactical strategy. PROS:  - Art style is nice - In-game animations are good CONS: - Poor gameplay - Simplified version of XCom - Weak UI - Clearly made for mobile - Weak story Such a nice style but weak content. If you are expecting an XCom-like, look elsewhere. If it had a deeper gameplay, reasonable PC UI, and story I would recommend it but this is not the case.", "appid": "1021070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039843270", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569931200.0}
