{"text": "This was an impulse purchase during the Steam sale.   Should've known to do a little more research, since none of the trailers or screenshots on their store page show actual gameplay, and their description doesn't really descibe anything about what type of game it is.   I assumed it was a platformer, but it's a point-and-click title.  And a very, very simple one at that.    More of an interactive movie than a game, really.  Machinarium, this isn't.   Gorgeous-looking game, for sure.   Just not my cup of tea.   I'm sure kids <12 and grandmas will adore every minute of it, though.", "appid": "314790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086763467", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1499601600.0}
