{"text": "TL;DR If you've never played before, it's a great game but I would wait for a bigger discount. If you've played it before, the improvements are so marginal it's not worth the price, imho. I was excited for this remaster, but man - when people said it's not that different from the original I didn't realize how on the money they were.  Agree with those who said if you've never played it, this version will be a lot of fun - get it on sale. If you've already played this, you will be wondering what has actually been improved when you launch it.  If the description is correct and the expansion adds \"5+ hours\" of new gameplay, doesn't feel worth it for the price right now.", "appid": "1041720", "steamid": "profiles/76561197989991815", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599652800.0}
