{"text": "I see why people like it. But this game has too many issues for me to recommend it. The gameplay seems to keep shifting to cater to more casual players. 70% of the time you will never see where you are getting shot from. Yea that's realistic, but not fun. This game badly needs the \"eye squint\" feature from Arma in order to zoom in on the landscape. Even a 15% zoom would help a lot. Also the emphasis on vehicles is a turn off. It's a lot less tactical when you can just send in a BTR (and aircraft/helis in the future) to capture points. The team with the most vehicles left will almost always win. Bottom line. Realistic? Yea. Fun? Not really.", "appid": "393380", "steamid": "profiles/76561197990876886", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1565956800.0}
