{"text": "I really like the setting and I'm also a big fan of souls-like games. But the controls are just so stiff feeling. It feels like there's a delay between what I tell the character to do and when he actually does it. I know the devs are trying to give the combat a weighty feel like how Dark Souls has, but this isn't how its done. I hope this gets hammered out in the final version, because I want to like this game more than I do right now.", "appid": "1243140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198023668268", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586433600.0}
