{"text": "I very much regret buying this game. I loved stronghold 2 and the rest of the Stronghold games. But this one was bad.... The online is unplayable (if anyone even plays it) and theres no skirmish mode (You vs. AI) At ALL! I love playing vs the AI on Stronghold 2. Its pretty difficult and fun to just try to build the ultimate castle and army. But theres no mode for this. Id love if there was a custom game mode creator where you could add AIs to verse on a map of your choosing and the settings of your choosing. But there is not. Luckily I got the game on sale. So i didnt get ENTIRELY screwed over. The campaign is okay. But I know most people like to have a competitive experience wheter it be with others online or against an AI. I for one would not recommend you buy this game if you like Stronghold 2 and are thinking this is level up and an upgrade from it. Most things are exactly the same. The only difference is the graphics (which are really great actually). All in all I can exaggerate enough how dissapointed I am.", "appid": "47400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047551000", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1388318400.0}
