{"text": "In my current and only game, I have reached the second town for the main quest. After talking with the elder as the quest asked I did not get any new quest objectives. I am now seemingly stuck to do endless bounty contracts which have you: A)Kill a Bandit Leader. B)Kill a Corrupted Leader. C)Kill the Necromancer Leader I have talked to many npc's who seemingly have something to say but never end up saying anything unique, I understand this game \"Early Access\" so one should not expect all that many unique quests, however I thought the main quest would not leave me high and dry with nothing to do out of the blue. If this is indeed just a bug, then I would have to lose all my progress of 8 hours and start again as this game does not allow multiple save files. If you are interested in this game, I suggest you whislist and follow the updates and dev blogs as they roll out. There is certainly huge potential here but do not purchase in hopes of losing yourself in a new fresh rpg.", "appid": "625960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198092114416", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1581076800.0}
