{"text": "This was for a long time one my favorite games. After the last patch, which happened some time ago, this came has become simply unplayable. The game is overrun with hackers now, who can not only see where every player is on the server but also what they are carrying and are armed with. You will not go more than two hours on any given server of decent population without running into, and more likely than not being killed by hacker. I don't mind dieing, honestly not at all. But eventually it gets old getting killed by people who teleport around with M4A1's and shoot through walls and the game stops being fun. Beyond the hackers a new product of the recent patch is constant freezes on server resets, game crashes and a plethora of other fun events. As the game is now, I wouldn't recommend buying it. This is a game that has been in alpha for an absurdly long time and yet seems to have made little to no progress. If anything things seemed to have regressed after this previous patch without any adressing of the issues it created or news of fixing them. All in all, this is a game that seems to have been forgotten by it's own developers. I held out for as long as I could, and told myself these problems would be fixed and it would get fun again. They haven't and it hasn't.", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198064325801", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1422187200.0}
{"text": "This game is still be labelled open beta/ early access. the bugs are numerous.  not worth the price with all of these negative things still present. CONS: -Random crashes -Random glitches into areas resulting in you being unable to escape/finish the dungeon -Server disconnections (the worse feeling when you're at the finish line)  -Placed into wrong servers (high latency, reconnecting and disconnecting multiple times to get the correct servers)  -Spells and attacks are unbalanced or glitched (where you might be handicapping yourself unintentionally, or you're very under powered) PROS: -Good spell variance for each weapon type -Spell customisation to make spells to your play style. -Combat very flashy Give this game another year.", "appid": "424370", "steamid": "profiles/76561197991548959", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582459200.0}
